 SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-256bae65-765d-44dc-bb32-587cd39b1a99\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223823819813/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6a6db80f-b034-4ee3-8805-2adadb96b4c3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223823819813/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-9f84f208-c36b-4fe2-a9ea-8c43b48a67f6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b2d632fa-c492-46fa-9ab5-4fa3a8ec05a2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223823819813/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c244183a-826f-423a-b610-f2359746a4dc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223823819813/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-74710ad1-5a38-433a-b3e8-d6ecce4a17d2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-840ca197-9266-404e-8422-27e4c8c2448a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-1e94f2e6-8ff6-4b16-8ee7-fe23595939eb\" style=\"\">북 커버 박스는 이렇게 제작하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a0aef290-5f11-4058-af37-f69408764c4a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7f3954e9-77d1-49b2-91be-bba5fe4edc3e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-99e893dc-6bb2-424c-9cb2-b3a4a4afcfd6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">어떤 용어로 불리든 간에 소중한 사람에게 책을 싸서 드리거나 또는 책이 아닌 다른 물건을 소중하게 포장하고 전하고 싶을 때 제작하는 인쇄물입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8a2bccfc-02e9-40c3-a4d7-8d20f3e5341d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e5b73813-2ddd-4b20-934f-ffcb07c3689d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-239e22d1-b480-4242-8246-23f561e45ddb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7972f1b5-c574-4554-b89c-9ac3faeef1f9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">형태는 봉투 형태이지만 다른 점은 높이가 있다는 것입니다. 봉투는 가로, 세로만 존재하는 인쇄물이지만 패키지는 장, 폭, 고가 있기 때문에 3차원(?) 형식의 인쇄물입니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5f51a717-a71f-471e-bcf5-9625780f1f37\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223823819813/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3580a44c-2642-474c-8a76-8ce5bceb7162\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8852f5e4-5093-48f0-b54f-c6cdefe44385\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ebadb731-62f2-4fe4-b29b-242e80663e4d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 이미지처럼 끼우는 봉투 형식은 가로, 세로만 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8eb20380-c1af-4fde-8bdd-96ed7541864f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0d7e46ac-1921-43cf-b7a9-f1dbeece115b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-46b2d821-9eb8-483b-9322-dce57c563db9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e1c9ef32-4e23-4fe2-8619-bfe8741aecb5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 오늘 설명하려는 케이스는 40mm의 높이가 있는 패키지 형태의 박스입니다. 하지만 독특하게 봉투처럼 뚜껑을 끼우는 그런 스타일입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-667cf24c-f200-481b-b02e-0d6dcbffebb2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223823819813/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-664c7a1d-937e-46dc-9df1-b8850175601f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ee908c8e-b53e-497d-bbb3-dda62a6e3acc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1c5419cd-3ae9-42ac-9c68-1e74e3d131d0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-159c5c5e-97cd-4962-a208-18f64decb948\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e923bcf1-a7e5-4014-b784-12a2a12473f4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-3f6e5772-0868-4c44-a5b1-ba37068122bd\" style=\"\">작업 일지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0fb0a4e5-6c5f-4319-a69c-0f522f71e9f4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-de80db6c-5b65-4b32-ac48-9dda4f54b8ce\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-12ea2697-646f-436c-93ff-690753736642\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>북 커버 박스</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4c57a41e-440e-48f6-a08a-5f3aa410a9f6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bda7cce8-9dcc-4d2e-a47f-5c685d115387\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e30289c1-9647-4d7a-ad44-dcf59288eeeb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7c706bff-f4da-44a3-9a4e-68d3d0eb5555\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aeb732a1-1ac6-4a56-b1b3-9ef6eb2faabc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 시리오 블랙 290g / 반누브 미색 227g / 슈퍼파인 324g</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-be044f68-a199-4899-b768-d4ab63b560a7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9ebdd224-3edd-4594-9e5c-de5c4baee9a8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d5aef29b-61f2-44e1-846b-85c04d2fdb66\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 140mm × 100mm × 40mm</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b74278d7-b2fa-4220-b8f5-2adffa026e2a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-aa4ffbde-1b66-42b8-ba7a-31051663fc3c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-58494453-36be-46b4-8b9f-a231357537cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 백색 인쇄  또는 단면 컬러 4도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f4b611b3-d167-4a42-87fd-06bc3bb534ba\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e3f09212-bb48-426d-a905-1c32e58f0db0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>코팅</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-171236ca-71cb-4814-ad0c-733221037209\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 슈퍼파인 종이만 단면 무광코팅 진행</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7a3c0439-2ca9-4a11-a1fb-5601dfe5b859\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-899c968b-243c-44a4-a2a5-0c8941747407\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0bd6ca02-5f77-478a-80ad-b42d7329a4f6\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 디지털 커팅</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0aca7761-ac25-4b84-93e1-763221958ee4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e1006da1-3cb5-4de9-bd32-81a622387412\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b1891cd1-e8a2-4be9-9612-54efcd820d4d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 샘플 각 5장 미만</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a8eae561-7f8d-43e8-abde-b321b47d7739\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e95da77c-c4c7-4880-8d32-147ac0336dea\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>금액</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-849d6f0e-34c4-4a40-a8e7-b84f2f7c8b2e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 업계 최저가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-ed763511-2d8e-4b9b-9ed9-d01d7d92258c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-79653ea6-c422-40dd-ad61-50c5ac06ad8e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-499b6c00-5b4d-44da-a324-fadd06ffafe7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-59dc1b90-5e05-4c52-807b-c210e75924c1\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>주의할 점</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6579ca6a-072f-4442-9c6c-b6d5c83f801a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-487616df-5811-4fd1-aab7-bc7e5642feb3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-99ffc29d-9cce-4ac9-ab3b-e090bd753dd0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0485368c-1f7f-447a-8d15-f4f687a29ef7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 작업 시 주의할 점은 다음과 같습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0520d079-427e-4f4c-9308-072a7a2ab87a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3ca0da33-1ec8-46b9-bd5a-dd34b98acfe9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e7f459e3-ea0f-4127-af61-f0a1bb18bdd2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2a8a8d40-d5a3-4b5d-8699-ff18fd6b29ea\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">뚜껑과 내용의 방향을 조심해서 디자인하십시오. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-449edcdb-8d58-43e3-a169-ef10f29417af\" style=\"color:#555555;\">경력이 오래된 디자이너라도 방향과 위치가 혼동될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a5296234-4d99-4ac2-8311-bf170bf65ae8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:539px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223823819813/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2f8594a0-c363-4fdd-9075-9169849ca938\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-749737bc-edd6-437e-af8b-90df6b32e2ec\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b9d1a888-4b98-4f7a-a1bd-9a2446da3b4d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1b533315-384a-4965-89a9-2d9556f6118b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c6efa546-613e-4130-af59-e40bfdfa43d0\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">뚜껑에서 덮개의 정확한 위치를 잘 계산해야 합니다.</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5611948f-2821-47e9-b5f6-091cece88ac2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 이 부분이 가장 헷갈립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-104b62f3-8517-4836-9704-d29665d8c0f4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a8497aa5-966c-4013-9e76-53f48d92304e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">쉽게 계산한다면 넓이가 100mm이므로 60mm와 40mm에 해당하는 위치에 꽂이를 만드는 것입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dbaeabac-8687-418f-b1e1-732585ea569b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223823819813/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-27e68d48-a6a6-4e22-82ad-0fa4826652b3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223823819813/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-515c19f9-b54e-432c-ad98-f2fe1f3b82f5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-59c122cd-1674-4288-a477-fa4bd410a0bb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-270848bf-b31d-42e9-a1c4-e1f89f48ac05\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 부분은 초보자는 잘못 제작될 수 있으니 (주)파파스컴퍼니에 문의하시면 칼선을 만들어서 제공해 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-21e3629d-edc3-4a40-bd49-88633896fc14\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-23fa6615-b196-4c25-a65b-1d53c433818a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-13a3cccd-861b-495c-a1df-4e532124335a\" style=\"\">요약</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4c465835-b31c-4603-a97a-a22da6cf4475\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-52f24f64-e424-433f-9840-d0f5c4077f91\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba5f15a7-ced8-4fbb-a702-617738fc6468\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>소량인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e84a9579-78db-42ce-bde2-7c6be7d419db\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-02341d17-69aa-4ef1-ae5f-6054d0c865c7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d0716c30-ee07-4769-bd19-b90e0c384a2a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 시리오 시리즈 검정/청/적, 슈퍼파인 324g 백색, 얇은 반누브 종이류 227g, 기타 종이는 상담 가능</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0c547d10-e52b-4c5a-9f0e-eeb2a842d87f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0d336ce1-fe63-48f1-b240-34513e093e14\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-de367c98-c522-4ad2-a3fd-f3bbb8df9815\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : A3 (420mm × 297mm) 안에 들어가는 전개도, 그 이상 사이즈는 별도 문의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-40f41d8d-b0b3-4121-99c9-4cdb4618113f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-283d4515-3a6b-427b-8f12-664d12708cff\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c1d958e9-638d-44ea-8aa0-e51b37924718\" style=\"color:#555555;\">: 컬러 4도 또는 백색 인쇄 (별색인쇄는 안됩니다.)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fa444920-c98d-4ef1-bee9-a35f8e81c254\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9898b1bf-926a-46a5-ac7a-f05cb1eea02f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>코팅</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e4ba9af7-6978-4aee-840d-e5fee5a6761b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 유/무광 코팅 가능</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-45953055-5411-4150-8bf4-a770c6815f80\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2990abca-0d19-4215-8264-779cdfca7c5d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dcccffb1-0dfd-4e5b-bb12-274585c8275e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 디지털 커팅</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-66c5d9d3-888b-4633-8004-e0529ae50723\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-63cb74fe-0214-4374-a477-e854751f57b5\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>수량 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5b8fc42a-956b-41c1-97ff-835144ea36fd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">: 1개 ~ 200개 미만, 200개가 넘어가면 오프셋인쇄가 유리할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c3c37c8d-3f05-4849-a541-574bc0398ce1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-50d81cd4-b50c-463b-bd57-02de008b8ee0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1a638646-659f-425e-a361-64cc6bad37d2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e787b1d3-3e0b-4e46-a94b-c571e714e908\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>대량 인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-112253ef-d2c5-4f84-8a2e-bd4858b824bb\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6fc135ad-0b4a-4eaf-a026-0d7a80e568d7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-00e99fa8-fb21-4f0d-966b-fe1b80ba1a79\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 마음대로 선택하여 작업할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7cd38408-028b-4c3e-8829-cd429559a760\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b9c34fbb-8d52-4499-a51f-60d6d3771164\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6f5cf10c-5f20-4134-9b28-5191f72be568\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : A3 (420mm × 297mm) 이상의 사이즈도 가능합니다. 병도 견적 문의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-60e75d71-7470-4e8e-813b-5b52b1a06bec\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-74bf7077-3130-4f28-bdcd-b5463398cce0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a8ba36cc-cf33-4c3a-865a-e59637f5eedf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">: 컬러 4도 또는 백색 인쇄, 별색인쇄도 가능합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-369390a2-7998-43ae-9cd4-ed8e99eb3552\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0be0afbc-028d-4d2e-bc3e-1a7d81109263\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>코팅</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c2982764-11e8-409f-bc81-e4dca099ebd0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 유/무광 코팅 가능</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-be081daf-2830-455a-afc9-bfab75ce712e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-70817bfa-f8e5-4568-b91f-d8a35b49c445\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>후공정</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1f610d15-00c2-4817-808f-e672c3ea7e33\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 목형 + 도무송</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ceb82868-daab-433d-9f2b-c8c1f3076282\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-559f5969-07d6-4d8f-9605-eb184ecb4ef8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>수량 </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-75ff4c33-06da-4d08-b60d-fca877a203fb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">: 200개 이상의 수량</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
